  "id": 791671157,
  "question": "编剧们是怎么把「地球人战胜有超科技的外星人」写的这么合理的？",
  "author": "山高县",
  "content": "<p>好莱坞初级阶段：</p><p>外星人放大炮啊！</p><p>马润军就拉大栓。</p><p>瞄了一瞄准。</p><p>打死个外星鬼儿。</p><p>俩眼一瞪就见了西天啊呀呼嘿！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-53f85fd6a5f9509bb64408919261c354_hd.gif?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"427\" data-rawheight=\"209\" data-size=\"normal\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-53f85fd6a5f9509bb64408919261c354_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"427\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53f85fd6a5f9509bb64408919261c354_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;427&#39; height=&#39;209&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"427\" data-rawheight=\"209\" data-size=\"normal\" data-thumbnail=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-53f85fd6a5f9509bb64408919261c354_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"427\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-53f85fd6a5f9509bb64408919261c354_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-53f85fd6a5f9509bb64408919261c354_hd.gif?source=1940ef5c\"/></figure><p>好莱坞进阶阶段，手撕外星太君：</p><p>阿米军放大炮啊！</p><p>外星人就拉大栓。</p><p>一炮打下去。</p><p>炸死他一大片。</p><p>俩眼一瞪见了西天啊呀呼嘿！</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-24ed8378d4f6af2cd29466de32c410de_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"426\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a1cf127ae6892cfbcccac88458cf2e_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-24ed8378d4f6af2cd29466de32c410de_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;640&#39; height=&#39;426&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"640\" data-rawheight=\"426\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-d9a1cf127ae6892cfbcccac88458cf2e_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"640\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-24ed8378d4f6af2cd29466de32c410de_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-24ed8378d4f6af2cd29466de32c410de_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></figure><p>好莱坞高阶阶段，感化外星太君：</p><p>收到以上信息的外星人请注意。你们收到的信息，是地球上代表皿煮滋油的国家发出的！这之前，你们可能已经收到了来自你们母星的信息，那是你们母星上的一个砖制势力发出的，这个国家与地球上的皿煮滋油为敌，企图把人类历史拉向倒退。希望你们不要听信他们的谎言，站在皿煮的一方，站在滋油的一方！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7ba148bd21b39128c99014ea0dfbafbd_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"799\" data-rawheight=\"173\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3629e193a921d78b983f4c72b001480b_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"799\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7ba148bd21b39128c99014ea0dfbafbd_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;799&#39; height=&#39;173&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"799\" data-rawheight=\"173\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3629e193a921d78b983f4c72b001480b_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"799\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-7ba148bd21b39128c99014ea0dfbafbd_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-7ba148bd21b39128c99014ea0dfbafbd_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4fe9348c09cb59422f0bd3d377b48605_hd.jpg?source=1940ef5c\" data-rawwidth=\"580\" data-rawheight=\"326\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-76b90235c54464ea721eeb38c329794f_hd.jpg?source